    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "* I agree for the sidebar fixed I've pushed a commit (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/5244bda2b8eb97465df2543648aadf686760edff)\r\n* Pushed a fix for the homepage hero on mobile (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/b9d1cf97f80e2a2085fdc54c8c37eadc1004ce18)\r\n* Also little fix for instantsearch.html markup (https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/d36b42ce536bcd93546ecafd6a56ec80e68ef223)\r\n\r\nAbout pushing ES6 we thought that advanced users who already know ES6 syntax will transform them by themselves. Since we do not target only this kind of users it might be easier for the more junior in JS. What do you think @redox @bobylito ?",
